channel.title: How do I change my cache in my client?
channel.description: I downloaded a cache and switched it out with mine but i get a error when i load my client up..can some please tell me how do I fix this problem...im updating my 317 stuff with with a cache for 400 or higher

item.title: How do I change my cache in my client?
item.dc:creator: @MrFun MrFun
item.description:
@MrFun wrote:

Onix:

You can’t just replace the cache and expect it to work. You’ll have to edit the way the client reads the cache etc, which I don’t have much of an idea how to do, since I’ve never done it before.

thanks, but i got that part down just don’t know “how” to change it
